<view class="page">
  <view class="mine-head card card-pad">
    <view class="avatar">凑</view>
    <view>
      <view class="item-title">周末轻装用户</view>
      <view class="item-desc">只找附近、免费、马上能去的小热闹。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section card card-pad">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text>步行范围</text>
    </view>
    <view class="item-desc">走太远就不像顺路了，先看近的。</view>
    <view class="distance-row">
      <view
        wx:for="{{walkMinutes}}"
        wx:key="*this"
        class="distance-chip {{preferences.walkMinutes === item ? 'active' : ''}}"
        data-value="{{item}}"
        bindtap="selectWalkMinutes"
      >
        {{item}} 分钟
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section card card-pad">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text>发现偏好</text>
    </view>
    <view class="pref-row">
      <view>
        <view class="item-title">只看免费</view>
        <view class="item-desc">没有消费压力，看看也行。</view>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{preferences.freeOnly}}" color="#ff8a3d" data-key="freeOnly" bindchange="togglePreference" />
    </view>
    <view class="pref-row">
      <view>
        <view class="item-title">不用报名优先</view>
        <view class="item-desc">到了再说，不先做承诺。</view>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{preferences.noSignupFirst}}" color="#ff8a3d" data-key="noSignupFirst" bindchange="togglePreference" />
    </view>
    <view class="pref-row">
      <view>
        <view class="item-title">安静路过友好</view>
        <view class="item-desc">不用硬聊，不用参与很久。</view>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{preferences.quietFriendly}}" color="#ff8a3d" data-key="quietFriendly" bindchange="togglePreference" />
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section card card-pad">
    <view class="section-title">
      <text>极简出门清单</text>
    </view>
    <view class="check-item" wx:for="{{checklist}}" wx:key="*this">
      <text class="check-dot"></text>
      <text>{{item}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
